</p><p>To see this, let <span class="mwe-math-element mwe-math-element-inline"><span class="mwe-math-mathml-inline mwe-math-mathml-a11y" style="display: none;"><math xmlns="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" alttext="{\textstyle x=a-n\left\lfloor {\frac {a-d}{n}}\right\rfloor }">
